	For other Vox Media coverage, see Vox.com.xml.


	CDN buckets:

		- d8wuu9msfgurd.cloudfront.net

			- ea-cdn.voxmedia.com


	Nonfunctional subdomains:

		- blog *
		- pixelpunch ²

	* Tumblr
	² 500


	Problematic subdomains:

		- ^ ¹
		- ea-cdn ²
		- jobs ¹
		- status ³

